{"repo": "roflcoopter/viseron", "pull_number": 1217, "instance_id": "roflcoopter__viseron-1217", "issue_numbers": [595], "base_commit": "199ed9ed87c2ef497506c8143c7def6615ed68df", "patch": "diff --git a/docs/src/pages/components-explorer/components/mqtt/config.json b/docs/src/pages/components-explorer/components/mqtt/config.json\nindex 9c9f33077..390fabc55 100644\n--- a/docs/src/pages/components-explorer/components/mqtt/config.json\n+++ b/docs/src/pages/components-explorer/components/mqtt/config.json\n@@ -33,10 +33,17 @@\n       {\n         \"type\": \"string\",\n         \"name\": \"client_id\",\n-        \"description\": \"Client ID used when connecting to broker.</br>Also used as the base for all topics.\",\n+        \"description\": \"Client ID used when connecting to broker.</br>Also used as the base for all topics, if <code>base_topic</code> is not set.\",\n         \"optional\": true,\n         \"default\": \"viseron\"\n       },\n+      {\n+        \"type\": \"string\",\n+        \"name\": \"base_topic\",\n+        \"description\": \"Base topic for all MQTT messages. If not set, client_id is used.\",\n+        \"optional\": true,\n+        \"default\": null\n+      },\n       {\n         \"type\": \"string\",\n         \"name\": \"last_will_topic\",\ndiff --git a/docs/src/pages/components-explorer/components/mqtt/index.mdx b/docs/src/pages/components-explorer/components/mqtt/index.mdx\nindex 9d99bfe9b..7296fd956 100644\n--- a/docs/src/pages/components-explorer/components/mqtt/index.mdx\n+++ b/docs/src/pages/components-explorer/components/mqtt/index.mdx\n@@ -48,7 +48,7 @@ You can observe the logs to find the entity ids.\n \n ### Binary sensor topics\n \n-#### `{client_id}/binary_sensor/{camera_identifier}_connected/state`\n+#### `{base_topic}/binary_sensor/{camera_identifier}_connected/state`\n \n Shows if Viseron is connected to a camera.\n \n@@ -78,7 +78,7 @@ Shows if Viseron is connected to a camera.\n </Tabs>\n </details>\n \n-#### `{client_id}/binary_sen